{"type": "article", "id": 2275, "title": "圣诞节蜡烛", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-10T01:08:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052223247o2y6gOWGscP91QA.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t对于丹麦人来说，圣诞节总是令人兴奋的。日前，丹麦设计师 Anne Lehmann 为丹麦设计品 Normann Copenhagen 设计了一款圣诞节蜡烛，燃烧时长达 88 个小时，灵感源自于巴黎的高级定制时装，Anne Lehmann 用最简单的黑色线条来记录天数，希望用户可以用点亮蜡烛的方式呈现一个不一样的假日氛围。定价 13 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.normann-copenhagen.com/products/normann-christmas-candle?v=330390\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222322bOLqFIDkzorYiGZR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.203125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605222322lwB5dLDSmIEox3sO.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}